    <div class="container text-center">
      <section class="mb-5">
        <a href="/featured-project" class="d-inline-block">
          <h2 class="Freckle-Face" style="color:rgb(205, 226, 12);font-size:3rem;">Featured Project</h2>
          <img src="/images/Plasma-Clouds.jpg"
               alt="Plasma Clouds featured project"
               class="responsive-image rounded shadow">
        </a>
      </section>
      
      <h1 class="Freckle-Face">Welcome to the Plasma Clouds</h1>
      
      <!-- About Artist Section -->
      <section id="about-artist" class="mt-5 pt-5">
        <div class="row align-items-center justify-content-between">
          <div class="col-lg-7 text-start">
            <h2 class="mb-3">Derrick Jarrell</h2>  
            <p class="lead mb-3">
              At my core, I am three things: an artist, a rebel, and an entrepreneur. Creativity and curiosity have always been my greatest loves, yet for much of my journey, I felt confined by structures that dictated how I should express them.
            </p>
            <p class="lead mb-3">
              Music has always been my first love—the sound, the why, the how—it is a part of me. Yet, the world of music has been changing. I realized I didn't want to be just another musician; I want to question, to innovate, and to reimagine the role of music and art in a shifting culture.
            </p>
            <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-warning mt-3">Contact Me</a>
          </div>
          <div class="col-lg-5 text-end">
            <img src="/images/about-artist-image.jpg" alt="About the Artist"
                 class="about-artist-image">
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>
    </div>
